        "subject": "LU-6801 lfs: add --data option to HSM migrate",
        "message": "LU-6801 lfs: add --data option to HSM migrate\n\nAdd --data to \"lfs migrate -H\" to let the user pass some options to\nthe copytool. This could be used to pass options such as priority,\ntransfer throttle, ... Added a test for it.\n\nThe format of the data is JSON, because internally lfs is passing the\nother parameters as JSON, so both parameters are merged.\n\nSigned-off-by: frank zago <fzago@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I97d3a34127365f08f29bfc8a96921f46da5d7e9e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
